name: The Fullness of Empty - Art Collection

metadata.name: The Fullness of Empty - Art Collection 1/88
metadata.description:
The Fullness of Empty Art Collection is a series of 11 pieces of art that accompany my album, The Fullness of Empty, which is currently available on all music streaming platforms. Every song has its own piece of A.I. artwork which was uniquely curated using the lyrics from each song.

Collectors who hold the TFOE Art Collection - AND - the BOY DAD NFT will receive a DRIP PASS which provides the following:
-Presale access to ALL future Splash Gordon drops, regardless of platform
-Early listening pass for future music releases
-Lifetime 11% discount on ALL merch featured on splashgordon.xyz
-Choice of ONE FREE beat, ONE FREE song mix & master, ONE FREE creative consultation (not to exceed 90 minutes) or an autographed physical copy of the TFOE Art Collection.

Thank you to any and all who make a place in their lives for my art to exist and flourish. I appreciate you beyond words. God is great, paper straight, nothing but blessings!
